{"tid":1547370,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"開撚完啲收到可靠消息求Fact Check Post未呀屌你老母臭閪","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:16:20.000Z","uid":11598,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"26e32cb13783ff5026e957d37f60aab5c5ca5479","tid":1547370,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/3noTy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2F3noTy.png&h=14d04d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇吓呢啲濕鳩post<br />\n<br />\n你班冚家剷日撚日開埋啲邊個邊個可靠消息<br />\n完全唔知你班撚樣有咩目的<br />\n屌你老母 同啲死廢老同意請轉發有咩分別<br />\n用吓個死人閪腦諗吓啦 個腦唔郁會生鏽㗎 好似啲廢老咁呀<br />\n明唔撚明呀 有啲嘢係Fact check唔到㗎<br />\n習近平啱啱WhatsApp咗我呀<br />\n你點Fact check 呀屌你老母 你唔打去國務院問？<br />\n用吓個閪腦啦 唯恐天下不亂<br />\n仲有啲係度推推推 白撚痴 睇完唔消化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我再講多次 不推文回覆 負評 上一頁 講完！<br />\n屌晒你班推post撚老母！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fb2e961abf8a607a6f4f0875d776ace96ff1231d","tid":1547370,"uid":6556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文回覆 負評 上一頁 講完！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5f52a9d61cbb60450680650647e24c30bb73bd74","tid":1547370,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d9e8f6c7026384705729eb96412255dbb0c7f7a0","tid":1547370,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"6102b59094fea04f7094d9c1ac361e2fa2f5104a","tid":1547370,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt